9:{"metadata":[["$","title","0",{"children":"Secrets of the Silent Witch | Global Drama Verse Guide"}],["$","meta","1",{"name":"description","content":"Monica Everett, the Silent Witch, is the world’s only practitioner of Voiceless Magic, a veritable heroine who single-handedly fended off the Black Dragon of legend. However, the young prodigy is actually…super-duper shy! Yup, turns out she only learned Voiceless Magic to avoid speaking in public. Ignorant of this, the Seven Sages have placed her on a top-secret mission to guard the Second Prince. Can Monica keep it together as she contends with both social interaction and the evils targeting the young royal?\n<br><br>(Source: Yen Press, edited)"}],["$","meta","2",{"name":"keywords","content":"KDrama,Anime,TV Series,Movies,Global Drama,Drama Guide,Watch Online"}],["$","meta","3",{"name":"robots","content":"index, follow"}],["$","link","4",{"rel":"canonical","href":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/anime/149973/secrets-of-the-silent-witch"}],["$","meta","5",{"property":"og:title","content":"Secrets of the Silent Witch"}],["$","meta","6",{"property":"og:description","content":"Monica Everett, the Silent Witch, is the world’s only practitioner of Voiceless Magic, a veritable heroine who single-handedly fended off the Black Dragon of legend. However, the young prodigy is actually…super-duper shy! Yup, turns out she only learned Voiceless Magic to avoid speaking in public. Ignorant of this, the Seven Sages have placed her on a top-secret mission to guard the Second Prince. Can Monica keep it together as she contends with both social interaction and the evils targeting the young royal?\n<br><br>(Source: Yen Press, edited)"}],["$","meta","7",{"property":"og:url","content":"https://gdvg-ten.vercel.app/anime/149973/secrets-of-the-silent-witch"}],["$","meta","8",{"property":"og:image","content":"https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500https://s4.anilist.co/file/anilistcdn/media/anime/cover/large/bx179966-g0EU7rVe2Og7.jpg"}],["$","meta","9",